{"tid":1934584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汪 明 荃 : 大 馬 疫 情 比 較 樂 觀，家 英 識 照 顧 自 己","createTime":"2020-03-20T04:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T05:11:31.000Z","uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"64fe53269b00b3990d0e020751083d4509e75cfb","tid":1934584,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎痠情持續，馬來西亞政府周三起對外封關。羅家英日前身在大馬拍英皇網劇《女法醫JD》，逗留當地一段日子，不過Liza姐汪明荃表示不擔心，而講到古巨基剛榮升做新手爸爸，同基仔相識多年的Liza姐，就向基仔送上祝福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/03/20200318_EN_%E7%BE%85%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%B1-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F03%2F20200318_EN_%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%258B%25B1-2.png&h=3cf06b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n本月初，羅家英在社交平台分享在大馬拍劇照片：「吉隆坡拍攝JD女法醫，兩個月，希望拍完疫情已過，一天光晒。」對此，Liza姐亦回應指：「大家要自己take care，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大馬疫情好似比香港樂觀，佢知道點樣照顧自己，而且佢拍攝時間相當長，頭尾差不多2個月時間。</span></strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/03/20200318_EN_%E7%BE%85%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%B1-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F03%2F20200318_EN_%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%258B%25B1-4.jpg&h=87026ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/03/20200318_EN_%E7%BE%85%E5%AE%B6%E8%8B%B1-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F03%2F20200318_EN_%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%258B%25B1-2.jpg&h=416d636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞琴日升100宗喎 <br />\n阿姐樂觀嗎?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PKakd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PKakd6.png&h=9fa81f90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTm4pFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTm4pFM.png&h=9f7c2037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMTuANX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMTuANX.png&h=b84671db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港未過300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpxK87r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpxK87r.png&h=257dc1c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"562b6452b575c7d2ff1ddbeea3cba07b8117c0f7","tid":1934584,"uid":81562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"冇GIF好失望"},{"pid":"b0f8d3d9b8caaddaac85156ee0b58ec5db0ea39f","tid":1934584,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"一張荃荃gif都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ca9e894888fde452b4d0b18966850eaca269ba","tid":1934584,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"聞西！"},{"pid":"61d0698911c725ad3e39f3a1dd355a7494180880","tid":1934584,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"諗起家英like -+莉ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d62570067e629fe42a99e37c0576c620860449","tid":1934584,"uid":275339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"冇gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cc44943a3c20bd69dc982cfcffc3405718302a","tid":1934584,"uid":106336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202