nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHXGaB3.jpg&h=381564a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心口掛住雪白無瑕嘅平安鐘與白綿綿嘅紙巾格外匹配<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH86mJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH86mJK.jpg&h=73e60e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有俊男相伴 阿姐更顯仙露明珠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xsKSRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xsKSRi.jpg&h=81c336b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xQTMcv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xQTMcv.jpg&h=ed710590&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ioicSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ioicSw.jpg&h=55684f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年齡對阿姐嚟講係一組組能破解嘅密碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3oVe7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3oVe7B.jpg&h=47f9b207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面上歲月痕跡、皺摺、暗啞、色斑都瑕不掩瑜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u6vkre8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu6vkre8.jpg&h=960cb7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人話頸紋就好似樹木嘅年輪般暗示歷史長久<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFQ8z8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFQ8z8Y.jpg&h=b3f67310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越多越深就代表閱歷豐厚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2e5CnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2e5CnH.jpg&h=4a218d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可幸阿姐靡顏膩理、滴粉搓酥，格外青春<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpZhtuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpZhtuV.jpg&h=9640791f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與慈禧般吹彈可破嘅肌膚永遠令人著迷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XrvOwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XrvOwK.jpg&h=1ded7b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豐姿綽約<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSUUvLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSUUvLG.jpg&h=b834a88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裊裊亭亭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VcyMi2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VcyMi2.jpg&h=e2913b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盈盈佇立<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG17QLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG17QLJ.jpg&h=bf502d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqbDc0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqbDc0A.jpg&h=e8af002c&s={SIZE}\" /></div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8ef169f1d677d108b604eaf4fbfdeba17cf09232","tid":1934584,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0f8d3d9b8caaddaac85156ee0b58ec5db0ea39f","tid":1934584,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"一張荃荃gif都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cAg0Day.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcAg0Day.gif&h=7884fa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"920059486cc541e7fbe29ecd28c7d00c9d698d82","tid":1934584,"uid":24160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a5cc44943a3c20bd69dc982cfcffc3405718302a","tid":1934584,"uid":106336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"明荃之友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>其實呀姐份人唔差嘅 算啦唔好狙擊佢</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmo