a.cx/i/BGisi8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGisi8a.png&h=3e6b9757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衫透哂成個波形出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哦~~<br />\n話要同大家介紹年盒喎<br />\n睇下入面幾多糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/STNdeHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSTNdeHg.png&h=0b8f49ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦 阿姐中門大開預祝大家新春快樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mf1tN2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmf1tN2v.png&h=96ee5a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪好想知呀姐點解咁 fit 咁大波??<br />\n原來阿姐識得玩fit ball 唔怪得又fit,又有波啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaXMzLJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaXMzLJ.gif&h=f2589b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姐仲專登請醉駕大隻仔仔教練教HIIT<br />\n但會唔會教壞我荃㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀姐好勁好掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAL2Syb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAL2Syb.png&h=ff76ce6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07mp5Td.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07mp5Td.png&h=44e5db57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2ZZUMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2ZZUMA.png&h=d2b5f445&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjjWcyg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjjWcyg.png&h=0bc946f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC8WWZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC8WWZY.png&h=a0c1a5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sOn8N6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsOn8N6F.png&h=45b03ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃荃45度傾斜唔容易㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n荃b 要小心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0e251dc726252a53b70acfc9fafa4c29bd281630","tid":1934584,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mZVWF7poRkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmZVWF7poRkY&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=bbe089d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mZVWF7poRkY</a><br />\n大馬樂觀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e318ea2bc804b178699757cbdb1bc69bb65e80","tid":1934584,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.share.photo.xuite.net/stacylife/1141cb1/4393042/167959391_x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fstacylife%2F1141cb1%2F4393042%2F167959391_x.jpg&h=e554a92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>羅家英今日西裝骨骨，為桂格燕麥拍宣傳片。家英哥透露聖誕節與阿姐汪明荃，去澳門度假？會否去骨場鬆一鬆？他即說：「不可以，危險，被傳媒跟到點算。（身痕想去揼骨？）現在不痕，年紀大，有揼骨但不身痕，我和阿姐都有互揼。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>問他現時會揼邪骨抑或正骨？家英哥坦言：「現在揼正（骨），幾十年前就當然有邪（骨）。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n家英哥又爆阿姐不懂弄巧手小菜，連蒸魚也不曉，只會煎蛋及炒飯，家英哥此言，不怕被阿姐扭耳仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家英哥梗係識照顧自己同細佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b4ad0fabeb9d7bb37a2180bc41f95827df233e","tid":1934584,"uid":50216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"羅家英要中<br />\n撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7347e73426796acf2c0a49087e2dd3127a76151","tid":1934584,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e318ea2bc804b178699757cbdb1bc69bb65e80","tid":1934584,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.share.photo.xuite.net/stacylife/1141cb1/4393042/167959391_x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fstacylife%2F1141cb1%2F4393042%2F167959391_x.jpg&h=e554a92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>羅家英今日西裝骨骨，為桂格燕麥拍宣傳片。家英哥透露聖誕節與阿姐汪明荃，去澳門度假？會否去骨場鬆一鬆？他即說：「不可以，危險，被傳媒跟到點算。（身痕想去揼骨？）現在不痕，年紀大，有揼骨但不身痕，我和阿姐都有互揼。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>問他現時會揼邪骨抑或正骨？家英哥坦言：「現在揼正（骨），幾十年前就當然有邪（骨）。」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n家英哥又爆阿姐不懂弄巧手小菜，連蒸魚也不曉，只會煎蛋及炒飯，家英哥此言，不怕被阿姐扭耳仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家英哥梗係識照顧自己同細佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Bb7SPmM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBb7SPmM.gif&h=13c3ce02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d074ea2fcc62304fc433e41e4efac245535906b2","tid":1934584,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e318ea2bc804b178699757cbdb1bc69bb65e80","tid":1934584,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"rep